beer.beer_description:
From recipe conception to cellaring, label design to packaging, this beer was created entirely by the wonderful women of Range Brewing. Generously dry-hopped with the 2020 Pink Boots blend of hops from Yakima Chiefs. Expect ultra fruity vibes carried in softly by a medium body. Smooth over the palate with mild and balanced bitterness. The finish is full of notes of grapefruit, orange and berry. Unbelievably drinkable.
Made by women, for everyone.

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 350 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 71!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 80 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 17!
